# Event Cancellation and Refund Feature - Walkthrough

## Summary

Implemented comprehensive cancellation and refund functionality for events, including:
- **Event Cancellation**: Organizers can cancel events with automatic refunds to all ticket holders
- **Ticket Cancellation**: Users can cancel individual tickets with time-based refund policy
- **Booking Cancellation**: Venue booking cancellations with advance payment refunds

